one "><div class="inline-flex items-center py-0.5 cursor-pointer rounded-full transition-all"><span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="w-5 h-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 5.653c0-1.427 1.529-2.33 2.779-1.643l11.54 6.347c1.295.712 1.295 2.573 0 3.286L7.28 19.99c-1.25.687-2.779-.217-2.779-1.643V5.653Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></div></div><div><div class="inline-block text-left" data-headlessui-state><button class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full  h-8 w-8 bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 dark:hover:bg-neutral-700 focus:outline-none" title="More" id="headlessui-menu-button-:R1spbbrqta:" type="button" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="h-5 w-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Zm0 6a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Zm0 6a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex-grow flex flex-col ms-2 text-lg rounded-xl sm:ms-3 sm:text-base dark:border-neutral-700"><div class="flex flex-col space-y-3"><span class="__className_7defe0 text-3xl lg:text-4xl leading-relaxed lg:leading-relaxed text-right">وَلَمَّا سُقِطَ فِيْٓ اَيْدِيْهِمْ وَرَاَوْا اَنَّهُمْ قَدْ ضَلُّوْاۙ قَالُوْا لَىِٕنْ لَّمْ يَرْحَمْنَا رَبُّنَا وَيَغْفِرْ لَنَا لَنَكُوْنَنَّ مِنَ الْخٰسِرِيْنَ</span><span class="__className_2abdee block text-md lg:text-lg text-primary-500 mb-3 sm:mt-3 sm:mb-4 dark:text-primary-300">wa lammâ suqitha fî aidîhim wa ra&#x27;au annahum qad dlallû qâlû la&#x27;il lam yar-ḫamnâ rabbunâ wa yaghfir lanâ lanakûnanna minal-khâsirîn</span><span class="block text-md lg:text-lg text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">Setelah mereka (sangat) menyesali perbuatannya dan mengetahui bahwa mereka benar-benar sesat, mereka berkata, “Sungguh, jika Tuhan kami tidak memberi rahmat kepada kami dan tidak mengampuni kami, pastilah kami menjadi orang-orang yang merugi.”</span></div></div></div><div class=" last:border-none border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 py-3 px-3 md:px-5 flex flex-col " id="150"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2"><span class=" text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-300 text-xl md:text-2xl">150<!-- -->.</span><div class="nui-ActionVerse "><div class="flex space-x-2.5 rtl:space-x-reverse items-center"><a href="/al-araf/150" class="__className_80e47c text-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-300 hover:dark:bg-neutral-600 hover">Tafsir</a><div class="nui-ButtonPlay select-none "><div class="inline-flex items-center py-0.5 cursor-pointer rounded-full transition-all"><span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="w-5 h-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 5.653c0-1.427 1.529-2.33 2.779-1.643l11.54 6.347c1.295.712 1.295 2.573 0 3.286L7.28 19.99c-1.25.687-2.779-.217-2.779-1.643V5.653Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></div></div><div><div class="inline-block text-left" data-headlessui-state><button class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full  h-8 w-8 bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 dark:hover:bg-neutral-700 focus:outline-none" title="More" id="headlessui-menu-button-:R1spdbrqta:" type="button" aria-ha