ir) yang tertinggal.\",\"juz_id\":8,\"surah_id\":7,\"transliteration\":\"fa anjainâhu wa ahlahû illamra'atahû kânat minal-ghâbirîn\",\"translation_en\":\"So We saved him and his family, except for his wife; she was of those who remained [with the evildoers].\",\"translation_de\":\"Da retteten Wir ihn und seine Angehörigen, außer seiner Frau; Sie gehörte zu denjenigen, die zurückblieben.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Bunun üzerine biz de, geride kalanlardan olan karısı dışında, hem Lût u, hem de ehlini kurtarmıştık.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Nous le sauvâmes avec sa famille, à l’exception de sa femme qui fut du nombre des anéantis.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":4,\"end\":8},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":23,\"end\":27},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":68,\"end\":70}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":82}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"83\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1038,\"number\":84,\"text\":\"وَاَمْطَرْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ مَّطَرًاۗ فَانْظُرْ كَيْفَ كَانَ عَاقِبَةُ الْمُجْرِمِيْنَࣖ\",\"translation_id\":\"Kami hujani mereka dengan hujan (batu). Perhatikanlah, bagaimana kesudahan para pendurhaka.\",\"juz_id\":8,\"surah_id\":7,\"transliteration\":\"wa amtharnâ ‘alaihim matharâ, fandhur kaifa kâna ‘âqibatul-mujrimîn\",\"translation_en\":\"And We rained upon them a rain [of stones]. Then see how was the end of the criminals.\",\"translation_de\":\"Und Wir ließen einen Regen auf sie niedergehen. So schau, wie das Ende der Übeltäter war!\",\"translation_tr\":\"Ve üzerlerine (taş) yağmuru yağdırdık. Bak ki günahkârların sonu nasıl oldu!\",\"translation_fr\":\"Sur eux Nous fîmes tomber une pluie (de pierres d’argile). Vois donc quel fut le sort des criminels.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":22,\"end\":27},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":30,\"end\":32},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":34,\"end\":36},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":38,\"end\":42},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":73,\"end\":74},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":79,\"end\":81}]},\"surah\":\"$2